---
import Layout from "@layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="点歌指南 | VoiceHub 校园广播">
    <div class="guide-page">
        <h1>🎵 VoiceHub 点歌指南</h1>
        
        <div class="guide-section">
            <h2>📱 如何使用点歌系统</h2>
            <div class="steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-num">1</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>访问网站</strong>
                        <p>打开 <a href="https://245959623.xyz" target="_blank">https://245959623.xyz</a></p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-num">2</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>登录账号</strong>
                        <p>班级账号：Seewo101 ~ Seewo122<br>初始密码：xlzwSeewo101（101对应102类推）</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-num">3</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>搜索歌曲</strong>
                        <p>支持网易云、QQ音乐、Bilibili 一键搜索</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-num">4</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>提交点歌</strong>
                        <p>点击“点歌”按钮，等待广播站审核</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <span class="step-num">5</span>
                    <div>
                        <strong>查看排期</strong>
                        <p>歌曲被选中后会收到通知，可在“本周热播”查看播放时间</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="guide-section">
            <h2>🎯 功能说明</h2>
            <table class="feature-table">
                <tr><th>功能</th><th>说明</th></tr>
                <tr><td>点歌系统</td><td>多平台搜索、歌曲投票、联合投稿</td></tr>
                <tr><td>排期管理</td><td>拖拽排期、时段设置、草稿保存</td></tr>
                <tr><td>班级账号</td><td>22个班级账号，独立管理</td></tr>
                <tr><td>通知系统</td><td>歌曲选中通知、系统公告实时推送</td></tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        
        <div class="guide-section">
            <h2>⚠️ 注意事项</h2>
            <ul>
                <li>请遵守校园广播管理规定，不点播违规歌曲</li>
                <li>首次登录请及时修改密码</li>
                <li>如有问题可通过班级群联系管理员</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="action-links">
            <a href="https://245959623.xyz" target="_blank" class="btn-primary">🎤 立即点歌</a>
            <a href="/broadcast/" class="btn-secondary">📻 查看热播</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</Layout>

<style>
    .guide-page {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 2rem 1.5rem;
    }
    
    h1 {
        font-size: 2rem;
        margin-bottom: 2rem;
        text-align: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
        background-clip: text;
        -webkit-background-clip: text;
        color: transparent;
    }
    
    .guide-section {
        background: rgba(30, 40, 50, 0.5);
        border-radius: 20px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        border: 1px solid #2a3a4a;
    }
    
    .guide-section h2 {
        font-size: 1.3rem;
        margin-bottom: 1rem;
        color: #b8d0e0;
        border-left: 3px solid #3b82f6;
        padding-left: 0.75rem;
    }
    
    .steps {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 1rem;
    }
    
    .step {
        display: flex;
        gap: 1rem;
        align-items: flex-start;
    }
    
    .step-num {
        width: 32px;
        height: 32px;
        background: #3b82f6;
        border-radius: 50%;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        font-weight: bold;
        flex-shrink: 0;
    }
    
    .step strong {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
        color: #b8d0e0;
    }
    
    .step p {
        margin: 0;
        color: #9aaebf;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    
    .step a {
        color: #3b82f6;
        text-decoration: none;
    }
    
    .feature-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
    }
    
    .feature-table th, .feature-table td {
        padding: 0.75rem;
        text-align: left;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #2a3a4a;
    }
    
    .feature-table th {
        color: #3b82f6;
        width: 120px;
    }
    
    .action-links {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: center;
        gap: 1rem;
        margin-top: 2rem;
    }
    
    .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        gap: 0.5rem;
        padding: 0.75rem 1.5rem;
        border-radius: 40px;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 500;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }
    
    .btn-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #3b82f6, #8b5cf6);
        color: white;
    }
    
    .btn-secondary {
        background: rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.15);
        color: #3b82f6;
        border: 1px solid rgba(59, 130, 246, 0.3);
    }
    
    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .action-links {
            flex-direction: column;
        }
        .btn-primary, .btn-secondary {
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .feature-table th, .feature-table td {
            display: block;
        }
        .feature-table th {
            width: auto;
        }
    }
</style>
